sentences.english: Gets and sets the number of items in the subtree under this group.
sentences.chinese: 取得及設定這個羣組底下樹狀子目錄中的項目數。

sentences.english: Maintains a write-ahead log in a subdirectory of the data directory.
sentences.chinese: 在數據目錄的一個子目錄中維護寫前日誌。

sentences.english: The raw directory may not be a subdirectory of the mount point.
sentences.chinese: 原始目錄不可以是加載點的子目錄。

sentences.english: That is, it works to a depth of one subfolder.
sentences.chinese: 即，其工作子目錄深度爲一。

sentences.english: Enable this option to search in sub folders too.
sentences.chinese: 啓用這個選項來在子目錄中也搜索。

sentences.english: Execute permission allows the user to enter the directory and access any subdirectories.
sentences.chinese: 執行權限允許用戶輸入目錄並訪問任意子目錄。

sentences.english: In the code above, the base case is built in the subdirectory for-loop .
sentences.chinese: 在上面的代碼，基本情況是建立在對子目錄循環。

sentences.english: Mouse capture is applied to a subtree of elements.
sentences.chinese: 滑鼠捕捉會套用至項目的樹狀子目錄。

sentences.english: The time-stamped subdirectories contain the published build results.
sentences.chinese: 帶時間戳的子目錄包含已發佈的構建結果。

sentences.english: Unzip the icons into a sub-directory.
sentences.chinese: 把圖標解壓到一個子目錄裏。

sentences.english: Will recurse through any subdirectories listed and include all assets inside them.
sentences.chinese: 將通過任何子目錄列表遞歸併包含所有資源。

sentences.english: Obviously, it's important to ensure all subgoals interoperate with one another with no issues or problems.
sentences.chinese: 顯然，確保所有子目標都順利地進行互操作非常重要。

sentences.english: The other three sub-directories are empty.
sentences.chinese: 其它三個子目錄是空的。

sentences.english: specifies the Drive letter and folder path to subdirectories
sentences.chinese: 指定子目錄的驅動器盤符和文件夾路徑。

sentences.english: Most of the configuration files that need to be changed are located in the subdirectories of resources.
sentences.chinese: 需要更改的大部分配置文件都位於資源的子目錄。

sentences.chinese: 確保所有的子目標都將順利地進行交互非常重要。
